quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  43,68,Ko onon yo jeyaa…ďe Am ! Kulol alanaa on hannde; wonaa on sunotoo…ďe kadi
  43,69,"…ďen gom…óim…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ďe woni jebbilii…ďe"
  43,70,"naatee ka Aljanna, onon e nanndu…ďe e mon, hi…óon sa…ónee"
  43,71,"[Golloo…ďe] hino wanngindinee e ma…ď…ďe, mirannji kaŇčŇče e √Īeddu…óe; hino ton kadi: kala ko wonkii muuyetee, gite dakmitoo. Hara le, ko on duumotoo…ďe ton"
  43,72,"Ko on woni Aljanna mo roninira…óon, sabu kon ko gollayno…óon"
  43,73,"Hino woodani on ton, muuyantee…ói …óuu…óu…ói, …ói √Īaamoton e mun"
  43,74,"Pellet, bom…ďe …ďen, ko ka lepte Jahannama …ďe luttoyta"
  43,75,"…ďe hoynantaake, tee hara ko …ďe ta∆īii…ďe ton"
  43,76,"Men too√Īaani …ďe few, si ko woni, ko kam…ďe woni too√Īu…ďe …ďen"
  43,77,"∆Āe nodda: \"Ko an yo Maaliku ! Yo Joomi maa gaynu fii amen !\" O wi'i: \"Pellet, ko on luttoo…ďe [ton]"
  43,78,"Gom…óii Men addanii on goonga kan ; kono …óuu…óu…ďe e mon, ko a√Īu…ďe goonga"
  43,79,Kaa …ďe e…ď…ďu feere ? Doo ko Men fewjoo…ďe
  43,80,Maa hara …ďe sikku Men nanataa gunndooji ma…ď…ďe e sirru ma…ď…ďe? Oo‚Äôowoye! Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen hino maandina takko ma…ď…ďe
  43,81,"Maaku: \"Si Hinaranko On no jogitii …ďi…ó…óo, ko min adotonoo rewude on"
  43,82,"Senayee woodanii Jey…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, Jey…óo Arsi kin; laa…ďu…óo e kon ko …ďe sifrotta Mo. @Corrected"
  43,83,"Accu…ďe …ďe jumpa, …ďe fija haa …ďe hawroya e √Īalaande ma…ď…ďe nde…ďe fodaa"
  43,84,"Ko Kanko woni On rewetee…óo ka kammu e rewetee…óo ka leydi, ko Kanko kadi woni √Ďee√Īo, Anndu…óo On"
  43,85,"Barke heewanii On Mo woodani …óum, laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji. Ko ka Makko anndal fii Darngal woni. Ko ka Makko kadi ruttete…óon"
  43,86,"∆äi …ďe rewata …óin gaanin Makko jeyah tefoore, si wanaa seedii…ďe goonga …ďen, hara hi…ďe anndi"
  43,87,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike …ďe, ko hommbo woni ko tagi …ďe? ∆Āe wi'ay: \"Ko Allah\". Ko honno non …ďe yiiliraa"
  43,88,"[Himo anndi kadi] fii ko (Nulaa…óo) on maakunoo kon: \"Ko an yo Joomi, pellet, …ďee ko yim…ďe …ďe gom…óintaa"
  43,89,"Awa yaafo …ďe, maakaa: \"Kisal !\" Aray ndebe annda"